Package view.Game

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    CellPanel
    The class Cell panel represents the view for one cell of the grid of the map.
    EastGamePanel
    The class East game panel is used in the map panel to allow the user to move around the map.
    EvolutionPanel
    The class Evolution panel shows a graphical representation of the wins and losses of a user.
    LosePanel
    The class Lose panel represents the view when the player loses the game.
    MapPanel
    The class Map panel is the JPanel that contains all other JPanels of the game view.
    MapPanelSouth
    The class Map panel south is used for the user to make their guess on who are the impostors and crewmates.
    PlayerPanel
    The class Player panel represents a cell of the MapPanelSouth panel.
    TableFrame
    The class Table frame is a JFrame used to show the JTable of the players from the log system room.
    WestGamePanel
    The class West game panel is used to pause the game or to open the settings.
    WinPanel
    The class Win panel represents the view when the player wins the game.
